"  BEEF","6  garlic cloves, minced","2 tablespoons roughly chopped fresh rosemary leaves","2 tablespoons olive oil","  About 1 tsp. kosher salt","  About 1/2 tsp. pepper","1  boneless beef chuck roast (about 2 lbs.)","  VEGETABLES AND COOKING","1  pint cherry tomatoes, stems removed","2  ears corn, cleaned and cut into thirds","1  onion, cut into 6 wedges","1/2 pound green beans, ends trimmed, cut in half","6  baby zucchini (1/2 lb. total), ends trimmed, or regular zucchini cut into chunks","3/4 pound thin-skinned potatoes about 1 in. wide","2 tablespoons butter","  About 3 cups chicken broth, divided"